data.description: A spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom country home with a bonus room, attached 2 car garage and a detached 1 car garage that may be used as a workshop.  It has ample natural light and cozy interior accents while settled on 12.19 acres with an ag exemption, barn and pond.  Mature trees.  Large covered front and back porches are perfect for entertaining.  It's fenced with pipe at the front with a gate.  Whether you're seeking a weekend getaway, a permanent residence, or a place to create cherished memories with your loved ones, this country home offers an incredible opportunity. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty of Texas while enjoying the modern conveniences of a well-maintained property. Don't miss the chance to make this country retreat your own slice of paradise. Schedule a viewing today and discover the charm of rural living in Fruitvale! New roof as of October 4, 2023.
